title: TRANSFORMERS - ROBOTS IN DISGUISE 022 (2013) (digital) (ImagesUn
description:
Transformers: Robots In Disguise #22

SOUNDWAVES!
The origin of SOUNDWAVE concludes as the master of sound confronts SHOCKWAVE in the ruins of Cybertron! Will they be friend -- or foe? Will the DECEPTICONS stand with SHOCKWAVE -- or will they join the AUTOBOTS? It's the moment of ultimate choice.

Written by John Barber
Art by Casey Coller, Andrew Griffith, Livio Ramondelli

25 Pages
Digital Release Date: October 30, 2013
Age Rating: 12+ Only
